item.title: CVE-2023-2330|2024-08-02T06:19:14.981Z -- unknown -- caldera%20forms%20google%20sheets%20connector
item.description: The Caldera Forms Google Sheets Connector WordPress plugin before 1.3 does not have CSRF check when updating its Access Code, which could allow attackers to make logged in admin change the access code to an arbitrary one via a CSRF attack
